data.description: This Rocklyn-built home exudes a fresh, like-new ambiance. Offering 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a 2-car garage, and a spacious loft area. Hardwood floors grace the main floor, including the staircase. The gourmet Eat-In kitchen features granite countertops, a substantial island, a roomy walk-in pantry, and 42' cabinets. Cozy up to the electric fireplace in the family room, complemented by coffered ceilings. The primary suite offers a spa-like experience with a sitting room, walk-in closet, separate tiled shower, and a garden tub. Upstairs, discover a loft/game room, a laundry room, and 2 additional bedrooms. This END UNIT is ideally located near shopping and restaurants, with easy access to the interstate. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! Awesome First Home, Great Rental  Agents please note, that should a buyer agent on the Lucido Global Team show a buyer and then buyer brings another agent to represent them, the selling broker commission will be 1% of purchase price.
